{"tid":1491342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣加油］唔係和勇合一！係不分和勇啊屌！","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:09:43.000Z","uid":150907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5772bb834c7a959e283d3de1f43536a2335bbd","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"睇返今日，各大派系出手想和理非同勇武切割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民：和勇合一<br />\n左派報：多得武警係深圳，阻嚇到一班暴力分子<br />\n大陸網民：民主爭取咪好，我支持㗎。<br />\n本地藍絲：睇到遊行示威終於同暴力切割<br />\n政府：大致和平，希望可以開展對話。<br />\n<br />\n無疑818，我哋贏到國際輿論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但實際上，五大訴求，一樣都未有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日各方出手，又想將示威拉去返和理非，然後，坐係度爭取到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問心，只係和理非爭取過乜嘢？阻止過乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到今天，仲可以咁成功，唔係和勇合一啊販民！<br />\n<br />\n係不分和勇，互補不足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFuck you Government, We can do it both！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n818展示我們從善如流，但你政府一日不解決！運動一日唔散！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山！唔會孤單！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac364cb0ee74c77f94401100a6c27521d26bed84","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"不要說 推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLet&rsquo;s say we can do it both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b1df5d2fb438ffcab3b5b2ac4c93a6bd45576c","tid":1491342,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"唔識用reddit/twitter嘅入嚟睇下!<br />\n<br />\n[ 整合 ]文 宣 國際戰線 ! 入嚟開工啦 !<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491304</a>"},{"pid":"88bc9186480d6ad63ed53e3899bc413899bd032f","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"不要說 推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLet&rsquo;s say we can do it both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90ffda403d43cfa5f47534236bd079a9447ef56","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"不要說 推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLet&rsquo;s say we can do it both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0619bee25b36cf8bbf1734ed304b58e7713d7348","tid":1491342,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:37:35.000Z","msg":"［文宣請入］！大家係時候要Connect班前線老散分化對家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491197</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"590f7acfd9f29c40624c6dc06b5f63389620fe9d","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"不要說 推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLet&rsquo;s say we can do it both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec116bda72283104b1586022182ec7131144dd54","tid":1491342,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"不要說 推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />